WebService-LastFM version 0.06
==============================

DESCRIPTION

WebService::LastFM provides you a simple interface to Last.FM Web
service API. It currently supports Last.FM Stream API.

CAVEAT

WebServices::LastFM 0.06 is now obsolete and doesn't cover all over the API
which Last.fm offers. It it currently being wored on to cover the newest
Last.fm API. A working 0.07 will be released shortly

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - LWP
  - Digest::MD5
  - Class::Accessor

